  <text x="100" y="188" fill="#3C3C52" font-size="11">(SPPS). Revolutionizes manufacturing. Nobel Prize in 1984.</text>

  <circle cx="80" cy="220" r="6" fill="#6E3B8A"/>
  <text x="100" y="218" fill="#6E3B8A" font-size="12" font-weight="700">2005</text>
